# Container SAST baseline — epic #448 / TRK-311 (Layer 1).
# Build context: components/da-tools/app/ (component-docker-build.yaml).
# Dir exclusions anchored (/) to this context root; *.md / *.log / .env*
# unanchored. build.sh runs on the host to assemble tools/ — it is not a
# COPY input, so keep it out of the image context.
/.git/
/.github/
/scripts/
/tests/
/docs/
*.md
*.log
.env*
build.sh
